	Document(content="Note: Hello everyone,The grades for Mini-project have been released for all sections on Brightspace. You can view your grade on Brightspace.If you grade on brightspace does not match with gradescope or you have some questions over the grade, please submit a regrade request. The regrade request deadline is by Sunday Dec. 15th. Please note that the regrading deadline is very short as we need to report your final letter grade. So, we strongly encourage everyone to submit a regrade request as soon as possibleThe regrade request submission steps are the following steps:If you believe there is an error in your grade, such as a score discrepancy between your Gradescope score and Brightspace score, please submit a regrade request to ece20875.purdue.university@gmail.com. You have until Dec. 15th¬†to submit this request. When sending your regrade request, please ensure you include:Section Number.Grading item (e.g., Mini-project).Purdue email address (if the email isn\'t sent from a Purdue account).Detailed reasoning or justification for the regrade, specifically referencing the README.¬† ¬† ¬† 2. If you believe there is misgrading for your homework problems, you can submit a regrade request on Gradescope.¬†Important: The regrade request emails not obeying the above instructions will be ignored.", meta={'folders': ['project'], 'title': 'Mini-project Grades released!', 'timestamp': '2024-12-14T02:31:05Z', 'user': 'jc6jsfzirna1eu', 'tags': ['instructor-note', 'pin', 'project'], 'likes': 2, 'views': 159}),
