	Document(content="Question: Does the formula for delta_0 have a negative sign? The slides seem to indicate that it does not have the -1, but on exams the formula used has the negative sign in it.¬† Answer: $$\frac{\partial E(x_i)}{\partial w_j}=-\delta_0x_{ij}$$ and,$$w^{t+1}_j=w^t_j+\alpha\delta_0x_{ij}$$", meta={'folders': ['exam'], 'title': 'SGD for single neuron', 'timestamp': '2024-12-13T14:18:09Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['exam', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 130}),
