	Document(content="Note: Hello everyone,The grades for Homework 7 have been released for all sections on Brightspace. You can view your grade on Brightspace.Note that, some of you have extensions with the instructor\'s approval. If you do and find your homework grade on brightspace does not match with gradescope. Please submit a regrade request with the instructor\'s approval message.The regrade request submission steps are the following steps:If you believe there is an error in your grade, such as a score discrepancy between your Gradescope score and Brightspace score or an approved homework extension that hasn\'t been accounted for, please submit a regrade request to ece20875.purdue.university@gmail.com. You have one week from the day the grades are posted on Brightspace to submit this request. When sending your regrade request, please ensure you include:Section Number.Grading item (e.g., Homework 7).Purdue email address (if the email isn\'t sent from a Purdue account).Detailed reasoning or justification for the regrade, specifically referencing the README.¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† ¬† For regrade requests, please adhere to the following guidelines:Send a separate email for each homework.Use the subject line: \'HW# regrade request\'.¬† ¬† ¬† 2. If you believe there is misgrading for your homework problems (e.g. the answer is right but marked as wrong), you can submit a regrade request on Gradescope directly.¬†Important: The regrade request emails not obeying the above instructions will be ignored.", meta={'folders': ['hw7'], 'title': 'Homework 7 Grades Released!', 'timestamp': '2024-11-19T15:12:56Z', 'user': 'kskmx82xa2s4ad', 'tags': ['hw7', 'instructor-note'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 118}),
