	Document(content="Question: For the \'repeater\' method, are we expected to use \'recursion\' and \'global variables\'? I can not seem to figure out how to approach this method since we are not allowed to input \'num_repeats\' into the \'ret_fun\' method as an argument. Answer: The inner function has access to the outer function\'s local variables. This means ret_fun has access to the variables in repeater including num_repeats. Recursion is not necessary", meta={'folders': ['hw4'], 'title': 'HW4 Problem 1', 'timestamp': '2024-09-19T02:26:48Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['hw4', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 119}),
